nge\": Yes or No.\n2. Select the sentences concluded Yes.\nDo not include the reasoning in the final output.\n\nRules:\n- Select AT MOST 4 sentences for the \"challenge\" aspect.\n- If no sentences match, return an empty list.\n- Indices are 1-based.\n- Return ONLY valid JSON.\n\nReturn format:\n{\"selected_sentences\": [list_of_sentence_numbers]}\nmodel\nthought\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```jsonjsonjson\nthought\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```jsonjson\nthought\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```json\nthought\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```json\nthought\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```json\nthought\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```</thought>\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```json\nthought\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```</thought>\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```</thought>\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```</thought>\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```</thought>\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```</thought>\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```</thought>\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```</thought>\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```</thought>\n```json\n{\"selected_sentences\": [24, 25, 26, 47]}\n```</"}
